name: Ryan de la Garza
bio: Ryan de la Garza is a comedian from Omaha, NE and a member of OK Party Comedy. His voice has appeared on Nerdist podcasts such as Terrified and Competitive Erotic Fan Fiction, and his body has appeared at comedy and music festivals like the Comedy Exposition in Chicago and The Fest in Gainesville, FL. He produces and hosts a variety of standup shows at his home base – Lookout Lounge – including the wildly popular Omegle comedy experience "You Had to Be There," featured at this year's Crom Comedy Festival in Omaha and the Bridgetown Comedy Festival in Portland, OR.
